            "title": "Presentation BAAL Beppie van den Bogaerde & Rob de Lange",
            "description": "We focus on the use of social media by deaf students in HE to circulate information, personal or related to their studies. They use closed and public groups to exchange information, in written Dutch or English and via short clips in their own sign language, or in International Sign. A survey of nine deaf users indicate they predominantly use social media in Dutch for public discussion, but more signed clips for closed groups.",
